attributes.review: It was glitchy, messy and made my phone heat up to an extreme state, causing it to freeze. There were times where I used the app and it immediately blacked out and forced me out of it. I’ve tried this about a dozen times and still the same thing. This app is just so worthless and not functional at all. I highly advise that no one downloads it. My phone is still pretty glitchy after using the app and now responds slowly when I’m on instagram, facebook, youtube, etc. after I deleted the app, everything returned to normal. This app is a whole MESS!!! Avoid it at all costs!!! It will ruin your mobile device.
